    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "the thing is i didnt check my monitor yet and i feel really lightheaded. i'm worried my sugar is actually way too high from the stress of the run and if i dont take something now it's gonna spike even more. isn't it better to just take a small dose now to stay ahead of it instead of waiting and risking a huge spike?",
